    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdminHomePage
    The AdminPage class represents the user interface for the admin user.
    AdminSetupPage
    The SetupAdmin class handles the setup process for creating an administrator account.
    Answer
    An object that represents user-submitted answers.
    AnswerManager
    Acts as a manager class for dealing with Answer objects.
    Comment
    An object that represents user-submitted comments.
    CommentManager
    Acts as a manager class for dealing with Comment objects.
    DatabaseHelper
    The DatabaseHelper class is responsible for managing the connection to the database, performing operations such as user registration, login validation, and handling invitation codes.
    DatabaseHelperTest
    This class consists of methods created to test various parts of database functionality.
    EmailEvaluator
    Used to evaluate/validate the input of an email address.
    EmailEvaluatorTest
    This class consists of methods created to test various parts of database functionality.
    FirstPage
    FirstPage class represents the initial screen for the first user.
    InstructorHomePage
     
    InvitationPage
    InvitePage class represents the page where an admin can generate an invitation code.
    Message
    An object that represents private messages.
    MessageManager
    Manages private messages between users (students and reviewers).
    MessageReviewerTest
    This class consists of methods created to test message sending/receiving and reviewer profile management functionality.
    MessagingPage
    Provides a UI for sending and receiving private messages between users.
    NameEvaluator
    Used to evaluate and validate the input of a person's first or last name.
    NameEvaluatorTest
    This class consists of methods created to test various parts of name validation.
    PasswordEvaluator
     
    PasswordEvaluatorTest
    This class consists of methods created to test various parts of password validation.
    Question
    An object that represents a user-submitted question.
    QuestionManager
    Acts as a manager class for dealing with Answer objects.
    QuestionPage
     
    Review
    An object that represents a reviewer's evaluation of a question or answer.
    ReviewerProfile
    Represents the profile of a Reviewer.
    ReviewerProfileManager
    Acts as a manager class for dealing with ReviewerProfile objects.
    ReviewerProfilePage
    Provides UI for reviewers to create and edit their profiles.
    ReviewManagementPage
    Provides UI for reviewers to view and manage all their reviews.
    ReviewManager
    Acts as a manager class for dealing with Review objects.
    SetupAccountPage
    SetupAccountPage class handles the account setup process for new users.
    SetupLoginSelectionPage
    The SetupLoginSelectionPage class allows users to choose between setting up a new account or logging into an existing account.
    StartCSE360
    A program that simulates a simple question-and-answer system.
    StringUtil
     
    User
    The User class represents a user entity in the system.
    UserHomePage
     
    UserLoginPage
     
    UserNameRecognizer
     
    UserNameRecognizerTest
    This class consists of methods created to test various parts of username validation.
    UserReviewsPage
     
    UserRole
    The UserRole enumerator is used to represent the different types of roles users can have.
    UserRoleTest
    Tests 17-19 focus on reviewing user promotion and role change functionality: - Test 17: User requesting reviewer role - Test 18: Instructor approving reviewer request - Test 19: Admin promoting users
    UserSubmission
    A parent class that is extended by the Question, Answer, and Comment classes.
    WelcomeLoginPage
    The WelcomeLoginPage class displays a welcome screen for authenticated users.
